reviews.review_text:
What were you thinking? If memory serves me correctly, I beleive this is the first Bertha after Jerry got busted in Golden Gate Park. It seems he was sitting there enjoying a little somethin' when a cop drove by, noticed there were old regristration tags on a BMW and stopped to check it out. He walked up, smelt something burning and saw Jerry try to hide something. Needless to say Jerry got busted.
  You'll notice the band and the crowd show a little more enthusiasm after the lines in the song about "why don't you arrest me" and "throw me in the jail house." Now you know why.
